description: Creates a new key value pair or replaces the value of an existing key.

parameters.name: KvsARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Key Value Store.

parameters.name: IfMatch
parameters.description: The current version (ETag) of the Key Value Store that you are putting keys into, which you can get using DescribeKeyValueStore.

nested_items.name: ItemCount
nested_items.description: Number of key value pairs in the Key Value Store after the successful put.

nested_items.name: TotalSizeInBytes
nested_items.description: Total size of the Key Value Store after the successful put, in bytes.

nested_items.name: ETag
nested_items.description: The current version identifier of the Key Value Store after the successful put.
